<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>323</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Vak thil tiem u lei hinkhuo hi,
 Mihing cheng leh ganhing cheng hi;
 Gitloh galina man zo tai,
 Lei hi manthai na gam ahi;
 Ni nuoia thil um cheng cheng hih,
 Bangmah lo mai ana hih ie.

[V2]
 Aw Lal Isu panglo in khawvel cheng hi,
 Bangmah lo mai ana hi ie.

[V3]
 2. Khawvel hauhsakna leh nawpna,
 A lopi leh hawihna chenghin;
 Thamuonna ahun tun thei puoi,
 Zie lei hansie dawl nuoi ahin;
 Thaklah ding him aum puoh ie,
 Bangmah lo mai ana hiu ie.

[V4]
 3. Khawvela hatna cheng cheng hi,
 Vanglai ni leh vullai nite;
 Chawm lokala tuoi ding ahiu,
 A nawpnau pumin a mang zing;
 Khawvela nawpna cheng cheng hi,
 Bangmah lo mai ana hiu ie.

[V5]
 4. Genthei liengvai chate chengin,
 Ka ngai ui nawpna leh muonna;
 Pathien Chapa Lal Isu chauh,
 Mangthaite di'n hinna ahi;
 A kawm ah nangle hung leh chin,
 Kumsawt hinna chu chang inla.</lyrics>
<title>Vak Thil Tiem U</title>
</song>